        Creates an Ibor cap/floor leg.

        The Ibor index should be EUR_EURIBOR_3M or EUR_EURIBOR_6M to match the availability of the curve data in IborCapletFloorletDataSet.

        Parameters:
        index - the index
        startDate - the start date
        endDate - the end date
        strikeSchedule - the strike
